data.title: Tabel Ukuran NPS - DN All Pipe Size
data.meta_description: Tabel Ukuran NPS - DN All Pipe Size - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls / .xlsx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides specifications for pipe sizes, including nominal pipe sizes ranging from 1/8 inch to 24 inches. It includes the outer diameter, wall thickness, and standard for various schedule numbers for each pipe size. The table contains extensive details on pipe sizes, outer diameters, and wall thicknesses according to different schedules.
